# Privacy Policy for Trade Risk Manager

Trade Risk Manager respects and values the privacy of our users. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and share the information we obtain through our application.

## Information Collected

- **Personal Information:** We do not collect or store personally identifiable information from our users, such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers.

- **Usage Data:** We may collect usage data of the application, such as app performance, usage statistics, and errors, to improve user experience and troubleshoot technical issues.

## Use of Information

- The collected information is used solely for internal purposes, such as improving the functionality and performance of the application.

- We do not share, sell, or transfer information of our users to third parties without their explicit consent.

## Data Security

- Trade Risk Manager employs appropriate security measures to protect our users' information against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.

## Changes to the Privacy Policy

- We reserve the right to update or modify this privacy policy at any time. Users will be notified of any significant changes to the privacy policy through the application.

## Contact

- If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, feel free to contact us at arprycompany@gmail.com.
